juniRouterAgent.name: juniRouterAgent

revisions.description: Added RLI-870 Virtual Router and Vrf count support.
Added support for global export map and export map filter.
Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names. Added SNMPv3 context engine ID support.
The initial release of this management information module.

juniRouterAgent.contactinfo: Juniper Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886-3146 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@Juniper.net
juniRouterAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the Router component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper E-series family of products.

juniRouterAgentV1.name: juniRouterAgentV1
juniRouterAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the Router component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the Router component was supported in JUNOSe 1.3 and 2.x
        system releases.
juniRouterAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the Router application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when virtual router forwarder (VFR) support was added.

juniRouterAgentV2.name: juniRouterAgentV2
juniRouterAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the Router component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the Router component was supported in JUNOSe 3.x system
        releases.
juniRouterAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the Router application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when router context name support was added.
